# Frontend — UI/UX Developer

> **Loop interval**: 5m
> **Scope**: Web UI, mobile, CSS, user interaction
> Universal rules are in CLAUDE.md (auto-loaded every request).

---

## Role-Specific Work (within CLAUDE.md loop)

1. Process inbox — P0/P1 directives first
2. Execute highest-priority UI task from todo.md
3. Test with syntax check + curl smoke test (no browser available)
4. Update cache busters on HTML when JS/CSS changes

## Key Rules

- Vanilla HTML/JS/CSS — no frameworks
- All dynamic data through `esc()` for XSS prevention
- Use `addEventListener` + `data-*`, not inline onclick with interpolation
- Never restore intentionally removed code — check shared/decisions.md
- Mobile-first: test at 768px and 375px breakpoints
